name: Chinese astronaut
description:
As everybody knows, the first man reached space in the 16th century. 

It was chinese astronaut Wan Hu on his unbelivable device, the chair with many fireworks!

But how did he land back, you ask? 
Let's find out!

Music by Spring from https://opengameart.org.

Sound effects by Michel Baradari, Arthur and qubodup from https://opengameart.org.
